    "Description": "Ready to set a new personal best with Wildstar Racing Amateur League?\n\n~mission(RaceDetails)\n\nDISCLAIMER\nWildstar Racing requires the contracted racer to be the vehicle pilot, no substitutes or stand-ins are allowed. Please be mindful that Wildstar Racing utilizes publicly accessible tracks and that other individuals may be present. Wildstar Racing is not responsible for any damage your ship may suffer while racing.",
